creator: GIMIN Studio
descriptionHtml:
Recording and monitoring expenses and income.
Reminders about periodic payments, e.g. rent, electricity / gas charges, etc.

Features:

- Payment and income schedule,
- Time reminders (weekly / monthly / yearly).
- Presentation of data on graphical charts in various modes,
- Handheld interest calculator,
- Configuration backup,
- Date list widget.

Copyright © GIMIN Studio
descriptionShort: Monitor/schedule your money. Payment/Income due date reminders.
